maven is a build tool
project management
Dependencies and versions
project structure (eg web-applications web-inf file )
build publish and deploy
 

** maven archetypes to define the project structure
   tells the folder structure for specific archetype like spring application or java application



 maven phases

 * validate runs automatically 
    checks everything in order validation checks
 * compile phase
 * test phase 
    where we run our test cases
 * package 
    package all the code and executes all the above phases and if any phase it fails completely
 * install
     install in the local maven repository

 * deploy
    pulishing the artifactory to the remote repositoty




scopes
-----------

* test
* copmpile
* provided



